{"tid":1099674,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[可能或者] 如何被 鄭源霖 查身份證 不失霸氣","createTime":"2019-04-10T02:25:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-10T02:25:50.000Z","uid":119330,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"bf7b105b30cf22a35958a367f36faaae2ae1f9cc","tid":1099674,"uid":119330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T02:25:50.000Z","msg":"【回帶】city仔好型<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/cwnHOT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/cwnHOT</a><br />\n<br />\n事源係睇左呢個post 諗起都市傳聞<br />\n鄭源霖入左學堂做督察<br />\n雖然唔知佢有無機會出街巡<br />\n但諗起佢城大反枱單野<br />\n如果俾佢攞到公權力<br />\n真心安已不<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/zGDIRTQ-xWY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FzGDIRTQ-xWY&d=se%2BVxgw3JrdCjNobn1OhIqVNHo2TAuuzEKoC36QvVjA%3D&h=e4929402\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/zGDIRTQ-xWY</a><br />\n<br />\n面對警察查身份證<br />\n首先要求對方提供委任證 以及所屬警局聯繫電話<br />\n用以核實對方身份<br />\n然後再投訴俾佢不禮貌對待<br />\n咁樣會唔會俾人打死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}